title: SATELLITE SAM 001 (2013) (Digital) (Vee-Empire) FRACTION/CHAYKIN
description:
Satellite Sam #1

The star of beloved daily television serial "Satellite Sam" turns up dead in a flophouse filled with dirty secrets. The police think it was death by natural causes... but his son knows there was something more? If only he could sober up long enough to do something about it.

This noir mystery shot through with sex and violence exposes the seedy underbelly of the golden age of television.

Published by Image Comics
Written by Matt Fraction
Art by Howard Chaykin
Genre: Crime
30 Pages
Print Release Date: Jul 3rd 2013
Digital Release Date: Jul 3rd 2013
Age Rating: 17+ Only
